metadata.name: VOYAGERS #42
metadata.description:
Generative animated painting made from looping gestures in a virtual void.

Voyagers is an exploration of automated gestures and screenspace layering effects. Each brush stroke sweeps through the canvas leaving a trail of color that either disappears or mixes with adjacent colors. The image slowly builds up to achieve an equilibrium between the rhythm of the gestures and the interaction of color values. These colors are quantized and dithered to produce chunky, textured, blocks of light that reify the materiality of the screen and the pixel. Two aspect ratios are possible, each with its own material relationship to screen-based work, 1:1 and 4:3 (vertical).

Press 's' to save looping animated GIF (live mode only).
Press 'p' to pause the animation.
Press 'c' to capture a single frame.
Made with P5.js and GLSL. By @galoandstuff.

metadata.name: Whirlwind #9
metadata.description:
The circle is divided into rings. 
The rings are divided into arcs. 
The whirlwind then colors and twists the arcs.

Variations:
- 1 circle on the screen
- grid of circles 2 by 2, 3 by 3
- several circles in the center of different radius
- the circles are arranged in the form of rays from the center

Dark/light background
Gradient/organized/chaotic colors of arcs
Organized/chaotic thickness of arcs

Please be patient. It takes a long time to generate. Thanks.

________
by neigal 24.05.2022

metadata.name: Mirage 001 #17
metadata.description:
Mirage 001-The first in a series of three works that explore 3D space, light, and composition. The animation takes 2.30min to complete the draw so sit back and enjoy. The first 30 collectors of the generative token will gain access-list to the next two Mirage releases. Please contact Zero Alpha if you wish to obtain a custom high-resolution file of your minted token. Thank you for collecting this work.

-3 Background environments
-9 Colour palettes each with 5 colours to the set
-2 Rare colour pallets

*This generator is optimized to be viewed on a desktop computer with decent GPU at
resolutions over 1000x1000px
*Reload the browser to start the animation from the beginning.
*2.30min to complete draw please be patient
